Preconditions:
The equation parameter must not be null.
The equation parameter must be a valid equation containing only '+', '-' operations, the variable 'x', and its coefficient.

Postconditions:
If the equation has a solution, return the value of 'x' in the form of a string "x=#value".
If the equation has no solution, return "No solution".
If the equation has infinite solutions, return "Infinite solutions".